This model is very different from the other ones I have created in the past, this particular model showcases good results in rendering vibrant and 3D fantasy images.

Moreover, it adeptly accommodates various levels of CFG without compromising the integrity of the image or excessively making it too sharp; This model supports well LoRAs, it effortlessly facilitates the creation of your desired outputs. Harnessing its capabilities, you can seamlessly bring your visions to life and achieve the results you seek.
